When the user asks to understand, map, document, reverse-engineer, audit, or create a complete atlas of a mobile application, read and follow:

`.cursor/skills/mobile-app-anatomy/SKILL.md`

Mandatory constraints:

- Use the deterministic ledger. Do not rely on a mental checklist.
- Start at cold process launch and recursively expand the route/action/feature frontier.
- Account for every project-owned file and every generated line shard.
- Maintain `not_tracked`, `tracking`, and `tracked_fully` states.
- Persist reports and evidence continuously.
- Never use sampling as completion evidence.
- Do not declare completion until `anatomy.py validate` returns `VALIDATION PASS`.
